In addition, incident photon-to-current conversion efficiencies (IPCE) for all three films have been evaluated under the monochromatic light illumination condition. The wavelength dependent IPCE calculations have been done according to the equation given below:1IPCE(%)=Iph(A)P(W)×1240λ(nm)×100\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
